pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: index.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: ' '
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:
    - styles.css
  toc: true
  variables: {}
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  editor: visual
  theme:
    - cosmo
  title: '-'
  title-block-banner: images/title_banner_frontpage.png
  listing:
    - contents: news/latest_news.yml
      type: grid
      sort: date desc
      fields:
        - title
        - date
